      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlamantli tlen neci quence poctli, quipiya atl huan eltoc ipan elhuicatl, tiquihtozceh huahcapan tlen iixco tlalli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
